<h2 id="chord-shapes-needed">Chord shapes needed</h2>

<p>With a capo on 3rd fret, this song requires all the common chords in the key of D (D, Em, F#m, G, A, Bm). You could play these conventionally, or you can use the alternate voicings which Iâ€™ll also show. The common way to play these chords is as follows:</p>

